high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter across the room that is between the stove and sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go across the room to the fridge that is on the right.
Open the fridge, cut the leftmost potato into slices.
Turn to the right and go to the stove that is on the left.
Put the knife into the pan that is on the front left stove burner.
Turn to the left, go to the fridge that is on the right.
Take a slice of the potato out of the fridge.
Turn to the right and go to the stove that is on the left.
Put the potato in the pot that contains the knife on the stove.
Pick up the pot containing the knife and potato from the stove.
Turn around, go to the door, hang a left and go to the black table.
Put the pot down on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a knife and slice of potato on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, again turn right and go to the kitchen sink
Pick up the butter knife on the counter to the left of the sink
Turn to your left, go forward and turn right to face the fridge
Open the fridge and cut the fruit on the left
Turn to your right, go to the stove
Place the knife upright in the tray that is on the stove
Go back to the fridge
Open the fridge and take a slice of the cut fruit
Go back to the tray with the knife
Put the slice in the tray
Pick up the tray from the stove
Turn right, again turn to your right, move across the room and turn left to face the table
Put the tray on the right edge of the table
anns.task_desc: Place a tray with a butter knife and slice of the fruit on the table

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife
Go to the fridge
Cut the potato on the left in the fridge
Go to the stove
Put the knife in the pot
Go to the fridge
Take a potato slice
Go to the stove
Put the potato in the pot
Take the pot
Go to the black table
Put the pot down on the black table
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a knife and a potato slice on the black table
